                    <span class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide text-purple-800 uppercase">Our Story</span>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-2 mb-6">More Than Just Scrunchies</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Peaceful Puffs began as a passion project in 2022 when founder Emily Rodriguez couldn't find hair accessories that combined both style and comfort. After years of frustration with hair ties that caused breakage and left creases, she set out to create something better.</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Each scrunchie is carefully crafted with premium materials that are gentle on all hair types. We believe that small details make big differences - that's why every stitch, fabric choice, and design element is thoughtfully considered.</p>
